e. Once it was lit, she sat down besides it and looked to the sky up at the stars. She felt lonely, very lonely these days, even though she somewhat had her family back, and thats all she wanted. She sat and watched to waves break on the shore, and waited...for what...she had no idea, but for something.:: <p>--=Amazon Strength is the only strength =--</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/02 5:43:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Beachfront</span><hr size=1> :: slowly walks toward her but stopping about 6 feet away:: do you always prefer to be alone?? hiding in the dark?  :: walks around the fire watching her:: you where gone along time, you left your family your tribe and then you snuck back in to SOT land and help Vel kidnap me and my children. <br>:: smirks:: nice way to say hi Mom, but then again you didn't say good bye but then again the last thing you said was &quot; i hate you&quot; :: watches her face:: i don't know why you hate me so, but it seems you do,i really am sorry about that, But like your other sister i seem to have let you down.<br>:: steps back away from the fire:: but then you really never gave me a chance, when you went from a baby to an adult over night all the mattered to you was Vel and not the mother that protected you as a baby <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umelousa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Melousa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/02 9:25:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> mom</span><hr size=1> ::Melousa heard her mother come near her, her stomach tightened into a knot, she knew how much Terrayus hated her, and she understood, she looked up as Terra spoke to her, a frown on her lips.::<br><br>&quot;No, I do not like to be in the shadows hiding, but it is here where I can do less harm. Mother, I know I hurt you, and I regret that, you dont know how much I regret everything I did, but I was confused, I was scared...I had all this power and I had no idea what to do with it. I know I treated you bad, I treated Vel bad too, I treated everyone bad, and I AM sorry about that. What can I do to show you how sorry? ::tears welled up in her eyes as she brushed a stray strand of red hair from her eyes:: I know I let you down, I let everyone down, Vel, you, and grandfather....and I want to make things right again, thats why I came back. I want to say Im sorry but I dont know how. I dont remember when Velaska first left, I was just a baby, but when she came back, i knew she could teach me how to use my powers, even though I would rather not. You speak of choises, what about my choises, I dont want to be part goddess. I want to be mortal, but did I have a say in that? Noo, I didnt.&quot;  ::she wiped at the tears running down her cheek.:: &quot; You didnt let me down, I let me and everyone else down.&quot;<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/02 9:52:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mom</span><hr size=1> ::a little taken back, she was expecting an arguement from her daughter, :::: I am sorry but as for the Goddess thing we had no control over that. But if you really want to give up that part of your life you can talk to Vel, She did it.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umelousa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Melousa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/02 10:18:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mom</span><hr size=1> ::She listened to her mother as her feet dug into the sand, toes wiggling.:: <br>&quot;Ive lived so long with them, and I hardly need to use them, mainly to heal those harmed. Ive grown attached to them.&quot;<br>::Her mother said nothing about her staing how she felt about other things, and she kept quiet, she was good at upsetting poeple, she did not want to do that again.:: <p>--=Amazon Strength is the only strength =--</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/02 11:50:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mom</span><hr size=1> :::looks at her daughter::: So daughter what are your plans? Are you going to stay or are you just passing through? Have you seen your sisters?  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A> at: 4/19/02 11:56:10 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umelousa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Melousa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#993300>(4/20/02 2:31:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> decisions</span><hr size=1> ::Melousa nodded as she wiped away her tears::<br>&quot;This is my home and I intend to stay. I talked to Tasha briefly, but her girlfriend showed up and interupted, so I came out here. As for my other sisters, I didnt know if you wanted teh rotten apple around them or not, so I have yet to see them, except on the boatride over.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#993300>(4/21/02 10:24:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: decisions</span><hr size=1>     Mel you are not the rotten appele of this family and i do thing you should see charish and erin. Thay need an older sister that they can look up to :: walks of to her holding her hands out to her:: you are a strong will Amazon and i am glad you are home <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umelousa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Melousa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#993300>(4/24/02 12:04:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> mommy</span><hr size=1> ::smiling, she walked to her mother and slid between her open arms, resting her head on her shoulder::<br>&quot;I'm glad you want me here&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uterrayus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terrayus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#993300>(5/3/02 3:10:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mommy</span><hr size=1> I am glad you came home :: holds her little girl:: you are my child and you will always have a place in my heart, Even if your sister Tasha believe I don't have one <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showPrevMessage?topicID=19.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showNextMessage?topicID=19.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm34.emailToFriend?topicID=19.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 